{"tid":1049062,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"對住啲自大撚 點樣先可以一招收佢皮","createTime":"2019-03-06T04:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T08:31:10.000Z","uid":140633,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7bec2fbe28c28482fe8782d438ea90f3dc8184","tid":1049062,"uid":140633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:25:33.000Z","msg":"自大撚成日都覺得自己啱曬 <br />\n永遠有佢講冇人講<br />\n<br />\n無條件相信自己所作既決定<br />\n即使到頭來食左屎<br />\n都係覺得人地做得唔好先搞到大家咁<br />\n而唔係質疑自己所作既決定<br />\n<br />\n永遠對自己有無限既信心<br />\n真係想問下佢哪來的自信？<br />\n<br />\n呢啲人永遠對耳仔都係閂撚埋<br />\n所以你講乜春都冇用<br />\n<br />\n萬能既連登仔請指教下<br />\n點撚樣先可以收鳩佢地皮 變翻做個正常人"},{"pid":"002686cf52b2d734cadde01f065dafea789c0c0b","tid":1049062,"uid":231951,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:34:32.000Z","msg":"喱撚埋一邊上連登出post，一定得"},{"pid":"6f286f582ec0eeef37eabf08f84e6eacbebfc7ad","tid":1049062,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"唔撚理佢"},{"pid":"0af70d6b8b612180eb72c042f1f983ee93a98704","tid":1049062,"uid":196077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"用呢個mode同佢講嘢 先聲奪人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/124741_b6d418aedcc477c6342db59635033036.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F124741_b6d418aedcc477c6342db59635033036.png&h=31c0bb41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93e08dffe1617ba737421461b381b1d369a2d076","tid":1049062,"uid":5343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:49:54.000Z","msg":"扮唔識 乜都比晒佢地做"},{"pid":"f818a08efe9b73bf8bfabf453e747563c03147eb","tid":1049062,"uid":107157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"睇錯大自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc07ab28ef24f5bc7fe77ae79c3a8bc7c260e9cb","tid":1049062,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu